hopobject.body: What do you do? health-healing-happiness.com ** Romanian construction materials producer Adeplast willlaunch an initial public offering for a minority stake duringOct. 2-15 on the Bucharest bourse, hoping to raise between 13and 15 million euros ($20.30 million). "The funds will be usedto finance new investments and develop the company's activity,"Adeplast said in a statement. The firm plans to sell 16.5million shares, or roughly 33 percent of its share capital afterthe IPO.
